    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<center><a href="https://sulfurandcu.github.io/">https://sulfurandcu.github.io/</a></center><br><a id="more"></a><h4 id="準備工作"><a href="#準備工作" class="headerlink" title="準備工作"></a>準備工作</h4><p><strong>創建一個站點倉庫 - 存放生成的靜態頁面</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>創建一個源碼倉庫 - 存放站點的原始代碼</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安裝 git 版本控制工具</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">略.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>重設 git 默認工作路徑</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># path : install_path/etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># normalize HOME to unix path</span><br><span class="line">HOME=&quot;*******************&quot;</span><br><span class="line">HOME=&quot;$(cd &quot;$HOME&quot; ; pwd)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">cd</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=&quot;$HOME/bin:$PATH&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># set Project Path</span><br><span class="line">proj=&quot;/repo/sulfurandcu.github.io.src&quot;</span><br><span class="line">cd $proj</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>生成密鑰，并將公鑰添加至賬戶</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C email@example.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安裝 node.js 運行環境</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">略.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>重設 npm 的默認工作路徑、默認緩存路徑</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set prefix &quot;d:\install_path&quot;</span><br><span class="line">npm config set  cache &quot;d:\install_path\node_modules_cache&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安裝靜態博客編譯工具</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli（installed to d:\install_path\node_modules\）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="生成框架"><a href="#生成框架" class="headerlink" title="生成框架"></a>生成框架</h4><p><strong>將源碼倉庫克隆到本地｜初始為空</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>在源碼倉庫中使用靜態博客編譯工具生成博客框架</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init（生成 \~\\node_modules\\, \~\\scaffolds\\, \~\\source\\, \~\\themes\\）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>附｜源碼倉庫目錄結構如下</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-  node_modules         # 功能依賴</span><br><span class="line">-  public               # 發佈目錄</span><br><span class="line">-  scaffolds            # 模板目錄</span><br><span class="line">-  source               # 源碼目錄</span><br><span class="line">    - _data                 # 配置</span><br><span class="line">    - _drafts           　　# 草稿</span><br><span class="line">    - _posts            　　# 文章</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    - archive           　　# 歸檔</span><br><span class="line">    - tags              　　# 標簽</span><br><span class="line">    - categories        　　# 分類</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    - img               　　# 圖片</span><br><span class="line">    - about             　　# 關於</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-  themes               # 主題目錄</span><br><span class="line">-   - landscape         # 主題1</span><br><span class="line">       - _config.yml    # 主題配置</span><br><span class="line">-   - next              # 主題2</span><br><span class="line">       - _config.yml    # 主題配置</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-  _config.yml          # 站點配置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>附｜常用命令</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init [path]                # 在當前路徑下生成網站框架</span><br><span class="line">hexo new  [layout] &quot;TITLE&quot;      # 新建文章</span><br><span class="line">hexo g                          # 生成靜態頁面</span><br><span class="line">hexo s                          # 部署到本地服務器，本地預覽</span><br><span class="line">hexo d                          # 部署到遠程服務器，在綫瀏覽</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean                      # 站點整體佈局效果改變時執行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安裝依賴"><a href="#安裝依賴" class="headerlink" title="安裝依賴"></a>安裝依賴</h4><p><strong>自動安裝 hexo 依賴</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;dependencies&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo&quot;: &quot;^4.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-index&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-category&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-tag&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-archive&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-renderer-ejs&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-renderer-stylus&quot;: &quot;^1.1.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-renderer-marked&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-server&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>手動安裝 hexo 插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-symbols-count-time</span><br><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-generator-feed</span><br><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-generator-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">npm install --no-optional --save hexo-baidu-url-submit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;hexo-symbols-count-time&quot;: &quot;^0.6.3&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-deployer-git&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-feed&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-sitemap&quot;: &quot;^1.2.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap&quot;: &quot;^0.1.6&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;hexo-baidu-url-submit&quot;: &quot;0.0.6&quot;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="博客遷移"><a href="#博客遷移" class="headerlink" title="博客遷移"></a>博客遷移</h4><p><strong>安裝配置 git 版本控制工具</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">同上.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>生成密鑰，并將公鑰添加至賬戶</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C email@example.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安裝配置 node.js 運行環境</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">同上.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安裝靜態博客編譯工具</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">同上.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>將源碼倉庫克隆到本地｜此時非空</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>執行以下命令自動安裝 pacgage.json 中的依賴</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package.json:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;hexo-site&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;version&quot;: &quot;0.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;private&quot;: true,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;scripts&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;build&quot;: &quot;hexo generate&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;clean&quot;: &quot;hexo clean&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;deploy&quot;: &quot;hexo deploy&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;server&quot;: &quot;hexo server&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;hexo&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;version&quot;: &quot;4.0.0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;dependencies&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo&quot;: &quot;^4.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-generator-archive&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-generator-category&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-generator-index&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-generator-tag&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-renderer-ejs&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-renderer-stylus&quot;: &quot;^1.1.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-renderer-marked&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-server&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-deployer-git&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-symbols-count-time&quot;: &quot;^0.6.3&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-generator-feed&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>下載 next 主題</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src/theme/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>拷貝 gitignore 中忽略的文件</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src/source/google**</span><br><span class="line">repo/oxoooooooo.github.io.src/source/baidu_verify_**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="開始寫作"><a href="#開始寫作" class="headerlink" title="開始寫作"></a>開始寫作</h4><p><strong>新建文章</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new [layout] &apos;TITLE&apos;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>頭部格式</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: TITLE</span><br><span class="line">id: uri</span><br><span class="line">date:  YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS</span><br><span class="line">updated: </span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- tag1</span><br><span class="line">- tag2</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- [category1, category1.x]</span><br><span class="line">- [category2, category2.x]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="部署網站"><a href="#部署網站" class="headerlink" title="部署網站"></a>部署網站</h4><p><strong>本地部署</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">https://localhost:4000/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>遠程部署</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">https://oxoooooooo.github.io/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
